A new release of the control / trajectory library for LabVIEW can be found here.

It contains a first attempt at aggregating individual VI documentation into both HTML and PDF form. The PDF can be access from windows Start Menu – Programs/Jasjunk … The HTML version isn’t installed as part of the package yet. It has to be copied to an empty directory from the github documentation folder.

It also contains a lot of changes to make it more compatible with its C/Java counterpart.

See the release notes and change log for a complete list of changes.
